{"tid":2176171,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯下週歸隊訓練 高文將他拒諸門外","createTime":"2020-08-27T02:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T05:07:50.000Z","uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c75de56df1ac0185cfb9dd8d177891c4a864a096","tid":2176171,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T02:40:22.000Z","msg":"欄哂球霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n  儘管已經決定離隊，但美斯（Lionel Messi）仍將在下週一參加巴塞隆拿的訓練，原因是他的法律團隊不想授人以柄。<br />\n<br />\n  美斯和巴塞未來有可能就合約條款問題走上法庭，為此，美斯方面要儘可能少的給對方以口實，如果拒不參加球隊訓練，將被視為違規違約之舉，如果未來發生法律糾紛，這對美斯是不利的。<br />\n<br />\n  不過，《TyC Sports》稱，巴塞新帥高文（Ronald Koeman）尚未決定，是否接受美斯和一隊球員們一起訓練，因為這可能對球隊氣氛產生不良影響，亦有可能單獨安排美斯練習"},{"pid":"80e12f8a8c62657dc85be7ae2db15b76efbb5a1d","tid":2176171,"uid":7854,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:03:26.000Z","msg":"廢老玩大左 以為人地會跪係度叫佢唔好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6442003890cab095d40831ad492be030ae84343a","tid":2176171,"uid":39133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:06:04.000Z","msg":"叫球王練習跳火圈"},{"pid":"a5e961a0516a6e9a14ebeeb2970467e1bd916f9a","tid":2176171,"uid":33660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6442003890cab095d40831ad492be030ae84343a","tid":2176171,"uid":39133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:06:04.000Z","msg":"叫球王練習跳火圈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a02bc642f8edfe2b12737a0c3841306873b24ba","tid":2176171,"uid":282509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80e12f8a8c62657dc85be7ae2db15b76efbb5a1d","tid":2176171,"uid":7854,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:03:26.000Z","msg":"廢老玩大左 以為人地會跪係度叫佢唔好走<img src=\"/assets